					<div class="site-header p-t-50 p-b-20 zoomIn animated"><h1>Questioner</h1></div>
					<div class="txt-l txt-w-l lh-2-0 text-left fadeInDown animated">Questioner çevrimiçi sýnav hizmeti sunar. Þimdi kayýt ol sýnavlar oluþtur veya öðrenci olarak sýnava gir.</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex-1 m-r-20 p-t-50">
					<div class="lg-form-c">
						<div class="form-pad">
							<form class="p-t-20 lg-form" method="POST" action="/login">
								<div class="form-i-con">
									<input class="inp" name="email" type="email" placeholder="E-posta">
								</div>
								<div class="form-i-con">
									<input class="inp" name="password" type="password" placeholder="Þifre">
								</div>
								<div class="form-i-con">
									<button class="btn btn-b btn-blue" type="submit">Giriþ Yap</button>
								</div>
								<div class="form-i-con">
